---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Douglas Linsmeyer.">
  <article class="page">
    <h1>About</h1>

    <p>
      I'm Douglas Linsmeyer. I lead digital technology at PING, in the Phoenix
      area — a software engineer who shifted into strategy without ever really
      leaving the keyboard. Before this I built enterprise web platforms at
      The Nerdery and RANT Sports, among other places. I volunteer with local
      coding programs when I can.
    </p>

    <p>
      This is where I write about things I'm working on, things I'm learning,
      and the occasional walk that turned into something.
    </p>

    <p>
      Find me on <a href="https://github.com/douglaslinsmeyer">GitHub</a> or
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/douglaslinsmeyer/">LinkedIn</a>.
    </p>
  </article>

  <style>
    .page h1 { font-size: 1.75rem; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem; }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
